cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL 

This paper deals with Arabic Documents Clustering, which is a task related to Information Retrieval (IR) systems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IR. The paper also proposes a method for text summarization using the Latent Semantic Analysis Model, which falls under the sub-categories of Natural Language Processing (NLP) and Machine Learning (ML), specifically cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.DL.
